Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 紧急事态
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大小姐
